assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Food Empire Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, engages in branding and manufacturing activities in the food and beverage industry. The company is involved in the manufacture, distribution, procurement, production, preparation, packaging, wholesale, and trade of instant beverages, snack food products, and food ingredients. It provides various branded beverages and snacks, including classic and flavored coffee mixes and cappuccinos, chocolate drinks, flavored fruit teas, bubble teas, infusions, instant cereal blends, and crispy potato snacks; and food ingredients, such as freeze dry and spray dry instant coffee, as well as non-dairy creamer. The company offers its products under the MacCoffee, CaféPH?, Petrovskaya Sloboda, Klassno, Hillway, Kracks, CafeRite, Bolt, MacTea, NutriRite, MacCereal, MacChoco, MacChocolate, MacFito, FesAroma, and Tazzanera brands. It also engages in the distribution, procurement, wholesale, and trade of beverage products; real estate and general trading activities; procurement and sale of raw materials, processed and non-processed food, and finished goods; ownership and leasing of factory space and equipment; marketing management services; and sale of rights to use intellectual property against royalty rights. The company sells its products to approximately 60 countries, including North Asia, Eastern Europe, South-East Asia, South Asia, Central Asia, the Middle East, and North America. Food Empire Holdings Limited was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Singapore.
